graph LR
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>React + Node.js + OAuth Proxy]

    %% External Dependencies (Infrastructure)
    Dashboard -->|runtime| NodeJS[Node.js >=18.0.0]
    Dashboard -->|UI framework| React[React 18.2.0]
    Dashboard -->|HTTP server| Fastify[Fastify 4.28.1]
    Dashboard -->|UI components| PatternFly[PatternFly React 5.4.0]
    Dashboard -->|K8s client| K8sClient["@kubernetes/client-node 0.12.2"]
    Dashboard -->|console plugin| PluginSDK["@openshift/dynamic-plugin-sdk 4.0.0"]
    Dashboard -->|authentication| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy Container]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|API operations| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    Dashboard -->|user auth| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server]
    Dashboard -->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    Dashboard -->|images| ImageRegistry[OpenShift Image Registry]
    Dashboard -->|builds| BuildService[OpenShift Build Service]
    Dashboard -->|console link| Console[OpenShift Console]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies (Platform Operators)
    Dashboard -->|monitor DSC status| DSC[DataScienceCluster Operator<br/>datasciencecluster.opendatahub.io]
    Dashboard -->|monitor DSCI status| DSCI[DSCInitialization Operator<br/>dscinitialization.opendatahub.io]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies (Component Integrations)
    Dashboard -->|manage InferenceServices| KServe[KServe<br/>serving.kserve.io]
    Dashboard -->|manage Notebooks| Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks<br/>kubeflow.org]
    Dashboard -->|manage ModelRegistries| ModelRegistry[Model Registry Operator<br/>modelregistry.opendatahub.io]

    %% Partner Integrations
    Dashboard -.->|validate| ISV[ISV Partner Apps<br/>NVIDIA, Anaconda, Starburst, etc.]

    %% CRDs Managed by Dashboard
    subgraph "Custom Resources Defined by Dashboard"
        OdhDashboardConfig[OdhDashboardConfig<br/>opendatahub.io/v1alpha]
        OdhApplication[OdhApplication<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        OdhDocument[OdhDocument<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        OdhQuickStart[OdhQuickStart<br/>console.openshift.io/v1]
        AcceleratorProfile[AcceleratorProfile<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
    end

    Dashboard -->|creates/updates| OdhDashboardConfig
    Dashboard -->|reads| OdhApplication
    Dashboard -->|reads| OdhDocument
    Dashboard -->|reads| OdhQuickStart
    Dashboard -->|manages| AcceleratorProfile

    %% DSC Operator consumes dashboard CRDs
    DSC -.->|watches| OdhDashboardConfig
    DSCI -.->|watches| OdhDashboardConfig

    %% Styling
    style Dashboard fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External Dependencies
    style NodeJS fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style React fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Fastify fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style PatternFly fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style K8sClient fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style PluginSDK fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style OAuthProxy fill:#999,stroke:#333

    %% External Platform
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style OAuthServer fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Prometheus fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style ImageRegistry fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style BuildService fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Console fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333

    %% Internal ODH
    style DSC fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style DSCI fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style KServe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Notebooks fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333

    %% Partner
    style ISV fill:#d3d3d3,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% CRDs
    style OdhDashboardConfig fill:#e1bee7,stroke:#333
    style OdhApplication fill:#e1bee7,stroke:#333
    style OdhDocument fill:#e1bee7,stroke:#333
    style OdhQuickStart fill:#e1bee7,stroke:#333
    style AcceleratorProfile fill:#e1bee7,stroke:#333
